article_id:1181,category_name:News,title_name:The 1.5-Year Anniversary Celebration Is Live!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/85b7aa8ad83687667c406e804d7cfdf6.png,message:<div>The 1.5-year anniversary celebration is live as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>.</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/dddbeca9bb4833c24201fbfaee465e10.png"></div><div><br></div><hr><div>1. Featured 5★ Adventurer Guaranteed! Two Platinum Showcases Are Live Simultaneously!</div><div><br></div><div>Platinum Showcase 1, where you&#39;re guaranteed to get one of the four featured 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurers as the tenth result of your tenfold summon, is live! Platinum Showcase 2, where you&#39;re guaranteed to get one of the three featured 5★ Gala Dragalia adventurers as the tenth result of your tenfold summon, is also live at the same time!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757599"></span></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1170">See here for more information about Platinum Showcase 1.</a></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1172">See here for more information about Platinum Showcase 2.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>2. Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia, where the initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6% from the standard 4%, is live! Also, Gala Alex is featured!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585807199"></span></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1168">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>3. Limited-Time Packs Are Here!</div><div><br></div><div>Limited-time packs are available in the Shop as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586757599"></span></div><div>Please check the Limited-Time Deals section of the Shop for details on each pack.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>4. Daily Free Tenfold Summons Are Here!</div><div><br></div><div>A daily free tenfold summon event, which will allow you to perform a tenfold summon on the applicable summon showcases for free once per day, started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585807199"></span></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1156">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>5. The 1.5-Year Anniversary Bonus Is Live!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/0c6fe055a3d8d99d0ed2dde97d453ee7.png"></div><div><br></div><div>The 1.5-year anniversary bonus started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div>For the duration until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586930399"></span>, you can get great rewards whenever you log in!</div><div>The details are as follows.</div><div><br></div><div>■Log-In Bonus Content</div><div><br></div><div>Day 1 Tenfold Summon Voucher x1</div><div>Day 2 Mini Zodi (Fully Unbound) x1</div><div>Day 3 Quality Honey x40</div><div>Day 4 5★ Wyrmprint: The Red Impulse x1</div><div>Day 5 5★ Summon Voucher (Adventurer) x1</div><div>Day 6 Blessed Ethon Ashes x40</div><div>Day 7 5★ Summon Voucher (Dragon) x1</div><div>Day 8 Damascus Ingot x1</div><div>Day 9 Eldwater x100,000</div><div>Day 10 Wyrmite x1,200</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586930399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>・The log-in bonus will be sent to your goodie box every day after 6:00 AM when you log in.</div><div>・Gifts sent as log-in bonuses can only be accepted for a limited time.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>6. Resetting the Social Reward in Co-op!</div><div><br></div><div>We will reset the number of times players can obtain the social reward, which can be obtained by playing co-op with another player for the first time, at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>.</div><div>After clearing a quest, you can get 50 wyrmite per player (up to 50 times). You can get a total of 2,500, so be sure to play co-op!</div><div><br></div><hr><div>7. Champion&#39;s Road Campaign Endeavors Are Here!</div><div><br></div><div>Champion&#39;s Road Campaign endeavors started <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span>!</div><div>Complete all of the limited-time endeavors during the event period, which lasts until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587362399"></span>, and you can earn great items and a total of 5,000 wyrmite!</div><div>The endeavors include Clear High Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial on Standard as well as Clear Volk&#39;s Wrath on Standard, and the notification below contains tips for how to clear those quests. Do your best to challenge those endeavors!</div><div><br></div><div>Note: If you do not have any adventurers who can be leveled up to complete the Raise an Adventurer to Lv. 80 endeavor, please wait for the raid event scheduled to start in the near future.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1587362399"></span></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1177">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>8. Dragalia Life Stickers Added</div><div><br></div><div>The stickers selected during the Dragalia Life survey about your favorite comic panels conducted between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1581314400"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1581487200"></span> have been added in-game!</div><div><br></div><div><a href="https://dragalialost.com/en/news/detail/1032">See here for more information.</a></div><div><br></div><hr><div>9. 1.5-Year Anniversary Upgrade Events!</div><div><br></div><div>Double stamina recovery speed event:</div><div>During this period, stamina recovery will be twice as fast.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586498399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Super flame-, light-, and shadow-attuned adventurer upgrade event:</div><div>The Flamehowl Ruins (Expert), Lightsunder Ruins (Expert), and Shadowsteep Ruins (Expert) event quests, where you can obtain items for upgrading flame-, light-, and shadow-attuned adventurers, are open for the duration of this event. Additionally, drop rewards you can obtain from Flamehowl Ruins, Lightsunder Ruins, and Shadowsteep Ruins will be tripled!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585893599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Triple drops for Brunhilda&#39;s Trial, Jupiter&#39;s Trial, and Zodiark&#39;s Trial event:</div><div>During this event, drop rewards you can obtain from Brunhilda&#39;s Trial, Jupiter&#39;s Trial, and Zodiark&#39;s Trial will be tripled.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585893599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Triple drops for The Imperial Onslaught (flame, light, and shadow) event:</div><div>During this event, drop rewards you can obtain from the Imperial Onslaught (flame, light, and shadow) will be tripled!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585288800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585893599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Super wind-, water-, and shadow-attuned adventurer upgrade event:</div><div>The Windmaul Ruins (Expert), Waterscour Ruins (Expert), and Shadowsteep Ruins (Expert) event quests, where you can obtain items for upgrading wind-, water-, and shadow-attuned adventurers, are open for the duration of this event. Additionally, drop rewards you can obtain from Windmaul Ruins, Waterscour Ruins, and Shadowsteep Ruins will be tripled!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1585893600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586498399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Triple drops for Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial, Mercury&#39;s Trial, and Zodiark&#39;s Trial event:</div><div>During this event, drop rewards you can obtain from Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial, Mercury&#39;s Trial, and Zodiark&#39;s Trial will be tripled.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586152800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586498399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>________________________________________</div><div>Triple drops for The Imperial Onslaught (wind, water, and shadow) event:</div><div>During this event, drop rewards you can obtain from the Imperial Onslaught (wind, water, and shadow) will be tripled!</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586152800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1586498399"></span></div><div><br></div><hr><div>Notes:</div><div>・These events do not apply to certain drop rewards, such as weapons, wyrmprints, astral pieces, fafnir medals, event items, or survival bonuses.</div><div>・Events described in this notification may be canceled or changed without notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1585288800,update_time1585214666